I"ù<p>Tools improvements are more about downside protection than upside maximization. Moving to Jira from Google sheets might help a good team track bugs better, but it won‚Äôt help a dysfunctional team improve its shipping velocity from 2 months to 2 weeks</p>

<p>Focus on processes, not tools</p>

